snippet.textDisplay: Dear CS @ mtv team. Pay no attention to what the critics say; there has never been a statue erected to a critic. Fantastic work till now. Probably 12-15 videos of current season will find a place in best songs ever in COKE STUDIO (both the version/country). It is a great moment to enjoy pure music, diversity,culture and every individual should possess the courage to applause something good rather having a negative attitude.
